author: dkhaywood
msg: bug 198: if invoke save() (through the NakedObjectProxy) then this will call validate; can catch an InvalidImperativelyException.  Note that this design mirrors then behaviour of the RCP viewer, but not - to be fair - that of the DnD viewer.
